block_list.body: Ever thought of owning a Yacht? Learn how to fold one, really simple in this video. This is the Origami Yacht designed by Toshie Takahama. Less than a minute origami. As usual, Enjoy!!! Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
